name: Unidentified_Jedi_(Form_VII_practitioner)
content:
A female Human practiced Form VII: Juyo / Vaapad, one of the forms of the lightsaber combat, at some point during the Galactic Civil War. She wore a robe resembling that of the Jedi apparel and wielded a blue-bladed lightsaber.
This character was depicted on the "Ataru" card of the Champions of the Force, the base set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, which was illustrated by artists Claude Bordeleau and Angga Satriohadi. Since the time period of the game is set around 0 ABY-3 ABY, it is uncertain whether this character may be identified as a proper member of the Jedi Order.
